ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無架啦..... 應該會比人賣上大陸支解</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 部野用左唔夠一個月就落得咁既下場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出咗 7 先買6s，就知樓主有幾窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e866f64219a225a527f36ab40228af3480d88dd9","tid":35722,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"幫你推下啦"},{"pid":"3bfa1174a8cdee5dc6da6c065acfa61b033a0b35","tid":35722,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無架啦..... 應該會比人賣上大陸支解</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 部野用左唔夠一個月就落得咁既下場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出咗 7 先買6s，就知樓主有幾窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  輕輕一推undefined</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁講 一陣比人屌 <br />\nAPPLE呢個牌子已經唔係代表窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我不嬲有儲蓄既習慣 上一部係G3 用左差唔多兩年半就壞撚左先轉IPHONE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0765f6efd881463ae8ccd312be51489e4943981","tid":35722,"uid":13233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"希望你搵到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好耐之前掛住同人吹水有條友係我個袋偷左我部電話都唔知 係過左陣隔離枱有個呀嬸話我知 佢仲話以為我同個個人識先無即時話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d814e136d22451caed8aca67be53ab7317f88","tid":35722,"uid":1937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"其實啲人執到iPhone 有咩用，又解唔到鎖，又賣唔到，好心就等機主打返黎啦"},{"pid":"120c657b0912ae21b7f5ae9f626a484675216aae"